data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own this 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath Cape Cod with approximately 1,159 square feet of living space as well as a partially finished basement! Features include an enclosed porch to sit on for tons of fresh air and sunlight, huge windows letting natural light and the sun in, a living room, a kitchen with built-in cabinets, a dining area, and a backdoor that leads to your screened porch to sit and relax on! The 2-car garage has more than enough space for storage! Conveniently located near schools, shopping, & everything Cleveland has to offer! TONS of Potential!! Being sold AS IS, WHERE IS, Buyer is responsible for all required inspections & certifications. All info & property details set forth in this listing, including all utilities & all room dimensions which are approximate, are deemed reliable but not guaranteed & should be independently verified if any person intends to engage in a transaction based upon it. Seller/current owner does not represent and/or guarantee that all property info & details have been provided in this MLS listing.
